step_data.thought: I'm now on the Export page in the Magento Admin Panel. Looking at the page, I can see the 'Export Settings' section where I need to configure the export options. To export the product catalog as a CSV file, I need to select 'Products' from the 'Entity Type' dropdown menu. Currently, it shows '-- Please Select --'. The 'Export File Format' is already set to 'CSV', which is what we want. After selecting the entity type, I should be able to initiate the export process. Let me first select 'Products' from the Entity Type dropdown.
